            "type": "HTML",
            "data": "<div class=\"markdown-body\">\n<h1>Comprehensive EDA — Arabic AI-Text Detection</h1>\n<h2>MSBDA-801 Big Data Analytics — Phase 1.4 + 2.3</h2>\n<p>This Zeppelin notebook generates the complete EDA visualizations required by <strong>Task 1.4</strong> (initial data exploration: structure, types, label distribution) and <strong>Task 2.3</strong> (word clouds, n-gram frequency, vocabulary richness — TTR) using <strong>Spark DataFrames</strong> on the Apache Zeppelin environment.</p>\n<h3>Outputs</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Data structure (<code>printSchema</code> + types + label distribution)</li>\n<li>Type-Token Ratio (TTR) Human vs AI</li>\n<li>Word cloud Human vs AI</li>\n<li>Top-20 words Human vs AI</li>\n<li>Top-20 bigrams (n-grams) Human vs AI</li>\n<li>AI-distinctive bigrams (AI fingerprints)</li>\n</ol>\n<h3>Prerequisites</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Spark 3.x runtime</li>\n<li>HDFS Parquet input at <code>hdfs://localhost:9000/user/$USER/arabic_nlp/data/processed</code></li>\n<li>Python libs: matplotlib, seaborn, wordcloud, arabic-reshaper, python-bidi</li>\n</ul>\n\n</div>"
