      "title": "3. Task 1.4 — Data Structure & Schema",
      "text": "%pyspark\n\n# === Print schema (structure + types) ===\nprint('=' * 60)\nprint('SPARK DATAFRAME SCHEMA')\nprint('=' * 60)\ndf.printSchema()\n\n# === Column types as a table ===\nprint('\\nColumn types:')\nfor field in df.schema.fields:\n    print(f'  {field.name:25} → {field.dataType}')\n\n# === Label distribution ===\nprint('\\n' + '=' * 60)\nprint('LABEL DISTRIBUTION (1=Human, 0=AI)')\nprint('=' * 60)\ndf.groupBy('category_encode').count().orderBy('category_encode').show()\n\n# === Per-subset distribution ===\nprint('PER-SUBSET DISTRIBUTION')\nprint('=' * 60)\ndf.groupBy('subset', 'category_encode').count().orderBy('subset').show(truncate=False)",
