            "data": "============================================================\nSPARK DATAFRAME SCHEMA\n============================================================\nroot\n |-- category: string (nullable = true)\n |-- text: string (nullable = true)\n |-- subset: string (nullable = true)\n |-- category_encode: integer (nullable = true)\n |-- cleaned_text: string (nullable = true)\n |-- processed_text: string (nullable = true)\n\n\nColumn types:\n  category                  → StringType()\n  text                      → StringType()\n  subset                    → StringType()\n  category_encode           → IntegerType()\n  cleaned_text              → StringType()\n  processed_text            → StringType()\n\n============================================================\nLABEL DISTRIBUTION (1=Human, 0=AI)\n============================================================\n+---------------+-----+\n|category_encode|count|\n+---------------+-----+\n|              0|33532|\n|              1| 2992|\n+---------------+-----+\n\nPER-SUBSET DISTRIBUTION\n============================================================\n+----------------------+---------------+-----+\n|subset                |category_encode|count|\n+----------------------+---------------+-----+\n|by_polishing          |1              |2851 |\n|by_polishing          |0              |11388|\n|from_title            |0              |11852|\n|from_title            |1              |138  |\n|from_title_and_content|1              |3    |\n|from_title_and_content|0              |10292|\n+----------------------+---------------+-----+\n\n"
